1. *Avion* je poleteo u 16:20. (The plane took off at 16:20.)
2. Videla sam *avion* preko leta. (I saw a plane during the summer.)
3. Ona se vozila *avionom*. (She traveled by plane.)
4. On je letio *avionom*. (He flew by plane.)
5. Da li su *aviokompanije* skupe? (Are airlines expensive?)
6. Ona je vozila *aviončić*. (She drove a plane.)
7. Otac mi je kupio *avionsku* kartu. (My father bought me an airplane ticket.)
8. Ima li *aviončića* na putu? (Are there any planes on the way?)